description: C. Beef Co. is making authentic Chicago-style Italian cuisine on the streets of Miami! This is the kind of taste you won't find just anywhere, and their Italian Beef Sandwiches, Risotto, Riceballs, and more are just what you need to satisfy your cravings for the finest food in town. An incomparable eating experience is right around the corner, so don't miss out on the very best food in Miami today!
